=== 签发HTTPS证书之DNS签发通配符域名证书

==== 签发通配符域名HTTPS证书（一）

[source, bash]
----
certbot certonly  -d *.xxx.com --manual --preferred-challenges dns --server https://acme-v02.api.letsencrypt.org/directory
----

.操作过程
----
